@courtyardmumbai puts together a sumptuous Shaadi By Marriott Wedding Brunch ✨
A curation of an elaborate food spread and décor in multiple themes, to give the to-be brides and grooms a taste of their wedding festivities. Wedding planning can be all consuming, a roller-coaster of emotions and an anxiety driven activity. And while Pinterest boards help, Courtyard by Marriott, Mumbai brings in a better way to visualise every detail of your wedding from Mehendi, décor, food and alcohol to wedding invitations and hampers. A Shaadi specialist will guide you through the details while introducing you to tailor-made wedding packages with some incredible perks and discounts.
.
WHERE?
Shaadi by Marriott Wedding Brunch
Venue: Courtyard by Marriott Mumbai International Airport
Date: 10th April, 2022 | Time: 12:30 to 4:00pm
.
Reach out to @courtyardmumbai today 💕
